{"tid":1375130,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"全港罷工無想像咁難！","createTime":"2019-07-28T03:38:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T03:42:20.000Z","uid":118888,"like":292,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"f0e08818b732b2728345e44ba68d265fb04d6c13","tid":1375130,"uid":118888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T03:38:30.000Z","msg":"「<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">其實我地呢刻人已經夠多</span><br />\n<br />\n睇到近日聲明都知<br />\n已經有唔少ao/eo都好憤怒<br />\n<br />\n罷工核心：<br />\n由政府公務員AO/EO做主導<br />\n港鐵車長/巴士車長配合<br />\n已令大部份打工仔無車番工<br />\n公務員起帶頭罷工作用<br />\n就算大財團唔跟<br />\n中小企都會動搖<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">只要人夠多</span><br />\n佢想炒哂你地？無可能架<br />\n200萬人遊行都試過<br />\n當你有100萬人罷工<br />\n就算罷一日都足夠比勇武衝10日<br />\n來得更有bargainning power<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔好諗喇<br />\n做唔到勇武既你地<br />\n罷工係你爬山既最強支援</span><br />\n<br />\n多你一個真係好多<br />\n要善用人多既好處<br />\n200萬人遊行無用<br />\n100萬人罷工？點解唔試！"},{"pid":"0894ed240f37749d3f703871936fcc277ffd15b0","tid":1375130,"uid":118888,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T03:41:54.000Z","msg":"200萬人遊行無用<br />\n100萬人罷工點解唔試？<br />\n<br />\nGood!!!!"},{"pid":"a22753ba32b4b9f649ba6807c2c05e16b71057c2","tid":1375130,"uid":118888,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T03:42:15.000Z","msg":"香港人醒呀<br />\n人夠多 無可能炒哂你地100萬人架！<br />\n罷工就算一日都好！"},{"pid":"3c63e01db654e5c0e6d98899d6ed528f15776565","tid":1375130,"uid":118888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T03:42:31.000Z","msg":"多你一個真係好多"},{"pid":"36a2165dc49601cc631e4a776b09e87088ede283","tid":1375130,"uid":118888,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T03:44:14.000Z","msg":"勇武唔到既我地<br />\n就用罷工直接影響大局<br />\n<br />\n要對得住勇武既佢地<br />\n我地既力量絕對不比勇武弱！"},{"pid":"4f518d60951dfa4edfb8aa18beee1e1f75770350","tid":1375130,"uid":129378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T03:44:15.000Z","msg":"全港大罷工"},{"pid":"f8138083112325918912daa2e89ebeb7a976ba20","tid":1375130,"uid":118888,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T03:47:13.000Z","msg":"出得多遊行<br />\n都會見識到人多有掩護好處<br />\n勇武既人好需要你地做掩護<br />\n掩護+勇武 相輔相成 缺一不可"},{"pid":"d0dba4ba23e98bd7e7578c0756c7565abd164b3d","tid":1375130,"uid":118888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T03:52:15.000Z","msg":"罷佢老味～"},{"pid":"bf56c646b1f279d7fe3ac5b700829dd7a3015f37","tid":1375130,"uid":164608,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T03:59:03.000Z","msg":"幾時"},{"pid":"5e091fcb131c0ebd02da9cbb173729257f22de9d","tid":1375130,"uid":118888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T03:59:36.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"b2485d6c648e55352e581479fa249a6c9b9a4054","tid":1375130,"uid":89184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:00:07.000Z","msg":"對， 其實如果令到 鐵路大罷工 好多人都可以有藉口唔返工（變相罷工）"},{"pid":"a54500866cbc12efc0820ab27d139c0330e2de9c","tid":1375130,"uid":177016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:00:20.000Z","msg":"私營機構抄鳩你<br />\n市場都係有個空缺<br />\n到時咪又係請人<br />\n要罷就罷一個禮拜<br />\n等班藍絲做野做到唔順氣自己遲或者一齊罷<br />\n政府工就穩公會啦<br />\n有公會吹你唔漲"},{"pid":"0bf14f83c4d0c7c9b9bb9b6266a5993d3571f6a2","tid":1375130,"uid":118888,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:01:06.000Z","msg":"義士已經拉得就拉<br />\n無乜人<br />\n所以罷工係最大力量令政府回應"},{"pid":"d170ae1e19dcb58fb0f9ce01996341c2e1dc278d","tid":1375130,"uid":258849,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:01:11.000Z","msg":"只要地鐵罷得起，全部人啲跟"},{"pid":"400b640c6b53afd9ed2f51a80dabf52f0ed82ac1","tid":1375130,"uid":261914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:03:27.000Z","msg":"一句講晒<br />\n團結就是力量"},{"pid":"4ec6234bca3e86fe561106682c16c60f733b552d","tid":1375130,"uid":118888,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"a54500866cbc12efc0820ab27d139c0330e2de9c","tid":1375130,"uid":177016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:00:20.000Z","msg":"私營機構抄鳩你<br />\n市場都係有個空缺<br />\n到時咪又係請人<br />\n要罷就罷一個禮拜<br />\n等班藍絲做野做到唔順氣自己遲或者一齊罷<br />\n政府工就穩公會啦<br />\n有公會吹你唔漲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:05:01.000Z","msg":"成功罷到一日<br />\n政府會非常驚你無限期罷工<br />\n即日出記者會回應喇！<br />\n而且開左個頭罷得一日又會有第二日<br />\n好似遊行咁遍地開花<br />\n而且香港人進化能力非常強<br />\n好似催淚煙，開左個頭，咩都唔驚！"},{"pid":"f41cfb3c81dd25c4458f232e0a888d11c545e1b8","tid":1375130,"uid":118888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:09:38.000Z","msg":"推比更多港鐵/巴士車長知<br />\n你地力量足以影響大局<br />\n鄉黑一家親 仲點容忍呀"},{"pid":"0f77afd6a172134ad07a49b57e617de3858924d1","tid":1375130,"uid":11698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:22:59.000Z","msg":"講得好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解上唔到熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc4786c9ffe79dc14730c6645f703e220d4768f4","tid":1375130,"uid":118888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:26:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"354d7a6861f66e02b80c0c82bdb4468452c7374b","tid":1375130,"uid":188482,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:27:23.000Z","msg":"最重要係過左bar正式公務員係唔會咁易炒到你&hellip;當然warning呢d一定唔少得&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢把天氣熱&hellip;出完街又入冷氣地方&hellip;好易病&hellip;成日sick leave就唔好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36d8a86e90ab669ab646b2b6d1567d5ce56e66c4","tid":1375130,"uid":167792,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:28:29.000Z","msg":"其實巴士地鐵一罷, 大把人跟, 都返唔撚到工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0e6eca74cbe5a54fea560559479faca948fabf0","tid":1375130,"uid":118888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:29:43.000Z","msg":"仍然要respect<br />\n一班勇武的年青人！"},{"pid":"1bad73cfa1fdf481d2c2a058245f45489c2ec18d","tid":1375130,"uid":169905,"l