0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:02:11.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"845a2a35460901f76057b48d273474a17510489c","tid":1375130,"uid":52566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:12:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8068993439ceb6bb9d415d6ab8a96cab04e318b","tid":1375130,"uid":118888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:21:51.000Z","msg":"罷工核心：<br />\n由政府公務員AO/EO做主導<br />\n港鐵車長/巴士車長配合<br />\n已令大部份打工仔無車番工<br />\n公務員起帶頭罷工作用<br />\n就算大財團唔跟<br />\n中小企都會動搖<br />\n<br />\n只要人夠多<br />\n佢想炒哂你地？無可能架<br />\n200萬人遊行都試過<br />\n當你有100萬人罷工<br />\n就算罷一日都足夠比勇武衝10日<br />\n來得更有bargainning power<br />\n<br />\n唔好諗喇<br />\n做唔到勇武既你地<br />\n罷工係你爬山既最強支援<br />\n<br />\n多你一個真係好多<br />\n要善用人多既好處<br />\n200萬人遊行無用<br />\n100萬人罷工？點解唔試！"},{"pid":"511443648995442b0342a41d9cdd1b7f8b655174","tid":1375130,"uid":118888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:22:22.000Z","msg":"救勇武唯一方法！罷工"},{"pid":"4913b0252ea016ac91e5f98cc1a522770cf44f81","tid":1375130,"uid":57929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:22:26.000Z","msg":"我會罷工"},{"pid":"4163b3ab06d19ba91fcf4f51d0ae164413951cd8","tid":1375130,"uid":129083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:22:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8e9319827eff606fddc158adf55804cb405ac36","tid":1375130,"uid":118888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:24:41.000Z","msg":"救義士唯一方法！！<br />\n罷工！！<br />\n不能再犧牲人命喇！"},{"pid":"ca05423d949793e3f9a64de9d47bc6044ab19a33","tid":1375130,"uid":227303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:25:47.00